snippet.title: Kakele Online - #MMORPG​​ | Trailer
snippet.description:
New game trailer! Come join us!

====================
Kakele Online is a Cross Platform, 2D open world massive multiplayer online role playing game. In Kakele,
you join players from all over the world to fight monsters, explore mysterious caves, complete 
tasks and quests, collect items and much more!
